A flowing river of glowing blue data streams winding through an abstract landscape, where each stream carries small geometric animal silhouettes (dogs, cats, various mammals) that pass through crystalline filter gates. Some silhouettes transform and change color as they flow through different checkpoints, while others fade away. The scene has a Studio Ghibli aesthetic with soft watercolor textures, dreamy pastel gradients of blue, purple and teal, and gentle magical sparkles where the filtering occurs. The streams converge into a serene pool at the bottom of the image, collecting the transformed shapes into an organized spiral pattern. Floating translucent geometric shapes suggest code structure without showing actual text. Warm golden light filters through from above, creating a sense of harmony and elegant simplicity.
